From: baur <baurzhansahariev@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Oct 2025 12:51:12 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Fix replication from translog for integral numeric values

---
 docs/appendices/release-notes/6.0.4.rst        |  3 +++
 .../reference/doc/lucene/SourceParser.java     | 18 +++++++++++++++++-
 .../reference/doc/lucene/SourceParserTest.java | 18 ++++++++++++++++++
